#

Grilled Shrimp Skewers with Mango Salsa and Cilantro Lime Rice

$25
450 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

Shellfish

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-ProteinLow-Carb

Tags:

GrillingTropicalSeafood

Description

Succulent grilled shrimp paired with a vibrant mango salsa and zesty cilantro lime rice, perfect for a tropical feast.

Ingredients

  • Shrimp (peeled and deveined): 1 lb
  • Mango (diced): 1 large
  • Red onion (finely chopped): 1/2
  • Red bell pepper (diced): 1
  • Cilantro (chopped): 1/4 cup
  • Lime juice: 2 tbsp
  • Olive oil: 2 tbsp
  • Garlic (minced): 2 cloves
  • Cumin: 1 tsp
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
  • Jasmine rice: 1 cup
  • Water: 2 cups
